About:

Dr. J. Byron Davidson, DO, is a board certified and fellowship trained Orthopedic Spine Surgeon who has specialized in evaluating and treating conditions of the cervical, thoracic and lumbar spine in our community since 2002. Although he believes surgery is the absolute last resort, his expertise is applying the least invasive surgical techniques to return his patients with degenerative conditions, fractures, deformity or tumors of the spine to their best quality of life possible. Dr. Davidson completed his medical school at The University of North Texas Health Science Center at Fort Worth, then went on to complete an internship and Orthopedic residency in Columbus, Ohio at Ohio University. He later completed a reconstructive spine fellowship at The Florida Spine Institute.
